{"tid":2206247,"cid":5,"subCid":12,"title":"愚夫愚婦 - 古德明","createTime":"2020-09-17T11:08:39.000Z","updateTime":"2020-09-17T11:08:39.000Z","uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":1,"replies":[{"pid":"f6ae6ba3b0a7ba57f1fe193e4516d204530f15cc","tid":2206247,"uid":25558,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-09-17T11:08:39.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200917/JZ7XMN6ZYZAQ7HEIF5MRPY4XJE/\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200917%2FJZ7XMN6ZYZAQ7HEIF5MRPY4XJE%2F&d=sV3HumZuViP2rFeoL7TNOL%2FjevXO%2BySp3REELKrGah4%3D&h=4aa75dff\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fcolumnist%2F20200917%2FJZ7XMN6ZYZAQ7HEIF5MRPY4XJE%2F&h=770a001b\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://hk.appledaily.com/columnist/20200917/JZ7XMN6ZYZAQ7HEIF5MRPY4XJE/</a><br />\n<br />\n節錄<br />\n<br />\n愚夫愚婦 - 古德明<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://hk.appledaily.com/resizer/k1WPt26o5CchU1ALrZO5IFrWm-M=/6720x4480/filters:quality(100)/cloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com/appledaily/BL5FRI3A6BBA3D7BA43YUVTIWU.JPG\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fhk.appledaily.com%2Fresizer%2Fk1WPt26o5CchU1ALrZO5IFrWm-M%3D%2F6720x4480%2Ffilters%3Aquality%28100%29%2Fcloudfront-ap-northeast-1.images.arcpublishing.com%2Fappledaily%2FBL5FRI3A6BBA3D7BA43YUVTIWU.JPG&h=ee31a633&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n肺炎瘟疫病毒全港檢驗期間，有小民在香港電臺自由風節目中說：「我當然參與檢驗，盡公民責任嘛！」香港真不少愚夫愚婦。<br />\n<br />\n香港小民自稱「公民」者，應先讀讀《公民權利與政治權利國際公約》，其中第一條說：「各民族都有自決權利，即可自由決定其政治地位，並自由發展其經濟、社會、文化。」第十九條說：「公民應有暢所欲言權利。」第二十一條說：「公民和平集會權利應獲尊重。」第二十五條說：「公民應一律有投票及獲選權利，以平等普選及不記名投票方式，參與定期籌辦的真正選舉。」。。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n又《公約》第七條說：「酷刑以及兇殘、不人道、損尊嚴的對待或懲罰，均不得施於公民。」第二十六條說：「法律之前，人人平等。」。。。。。。<br />\n<br />\n「公民」或citizenship這個觀念，是「西方玩意」，所以，我黨從來沒有批准實施《公民權利與政治權利國際公約》。。。。。。。"}]}